metadata.name: Night Watch
metadata.description:
1/1 Night Watch by @maxlarsson  
Unique Collection

This is the first piece released in the collection "Bon Voyage". 

Location: Dakar, Senegal in 2015. 

I was in Dakar for a photo shoot but I also had time to explore the city. One evening  we met some super cool and inspiring locals and they asked us to join them. We ended up at a rooftop after sunset and watched the city come to life. 

(8424 × 5266 High resolution photo will be delivered to the collector after the purchase.)
